<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA50">
<l>ariyapula ṉaintaṭakki yāymalarkoṇ ṭārvam</l>
<l>puriyap pariciṉāṟ pulkiṟ – periyaṉāy</l>
<l>māṟṟātu vīṟṟirunta māvalipāl vaṇkainī</l>
<l>rēṟṟāṉaik kāṇpa teḷitu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one embraces [him] by means of practising devotion</l>
<l>with choice flowers, repressing the five senses difficult [to control],</l>
<l>it is easy to see the one who received in [his] generous hand water</l>
<l>from Māvali who unchangeably sat enthroned as a great man.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
